 firefox-esr | firefox-esr:any | firefox-esr:armhf | firefox | www-browser | www-browser:any,
 firefox-esr-l10n-tr,
 iw,
 pardus-backgrounds,
 plymouth,
 plymouth-themes,
 tlp,
 xdg-utils
Description: Meta-package with dependencies common to all desktops provided by Pardus
 This metapackage depends on Pardus packages that should be intalled on all
 desktop installations of Pardus.
 .
 This metapackage is a dependency of all pardus-*-desktop packages.


